name: consumer.is.me
description:
Packaging, brands and logos are all consumerism in my mind. Brand promises, shiny design, yellow stamps with of facts, the 'organic' ingredients visualized; all to seduce people. Then we re-read our state, we realize consumerism = konsumerisme
konsumer is me
consumer is me
consumer = me
consumer.is.me

Analog collage made from paper trash on canvas board made on September 2019
